channel.title: Hello Guys I'm new to mopar!
channel.description: Hello, my name in all runescape private servers that i played has been: Logic, i am 17 years old and I have recently took interest in creating a runescape private server. But I have no clue how to do it my friend told me to come here and look up guides and ask questions. well that's what I am here to do i guess.
